{"tid":1539700,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[屌佢老母又自己人查自己人] 林定國、余黎青萍","createTime":"2019-09-04T10:16:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T10:22:28.000Z","uid":45652,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d20a54ea234285535ae7db7a1abf685687373c64","tid":1539700,"uid":45652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:16:36.000Z","msg":"資深大律師<span style=\"color: red;\">林定國</span>近年突然高調縱橫政法界，最為人熟悉是他出任大律師公會主席期間，<span style=\"color: red;\">被質疑未有為業界發聲，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">取態不鮮明</span>，遭公會前主席、資深大律師戴啟思成功挑戰</span>，結果無緣連任。不過，他仕途繼續看漲，甚至一度傳出是律政司司長人選，雖然沒有成事，但卻於本年元旦日起獲政府委任為消費者委員會主席。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.singpao.com.hk/index.php?fi=news1&amp;id=96790\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.singpao.com.hk%2Findex.php%3Ffi%3Dnews1%26id%3D96790&d=vI%2FQCok0BRDS6jHm%2BKkcam6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=44d3fcae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.singpao.com.hk/index.php?fi=news1&amp;id=96790</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭月娥參選時擔任其競選辦<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">資深顧問</span>的前高官余黎青萍</span>的相關言論，本來是發表在前政務官的群組上。余黎青萍在訊息內提出「四不」做法。第一，不適合設立調查委員會，因為此舉會繞過現行處理這類事情的機構；第二，不適合進行特赦，因為這會損害合法拘捕及檢控的體系以及摑了警方一巴；第三，不適合放棄公平的司法審訊；第四，不適合向那個「瞓身」尋求外國支持以對付自己城巿的人的說辭退讓。她表示，做出上述四項中的任何一項都是最不適當，並且是對支持政府的沉默大多數的最大蔑視。最後，她更表示對曾經備受政務官尊崇的陳方安生「完全失望」<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1532550/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1532550%2F&d=vI%2FQCok0BRDS6jHm%2BKkcam6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=bebae0c4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1532550%2F&h=abb3e902\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1532550/</a><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母又係自己人查自己人"},{"pid":"42ec6cc4704725189d2462ade61139f5459809d1","tid":1539700,"uid":121985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:17:46.000Z","msg":"預撚咗啦屌佢老母臭閪<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"38612a6b944a186c36ba5de5f13bd197d7d454cf","tid":1539700,"uid":16956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:22:28.000Z","msg":"藍上加藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}